Annotation Interface ClassInfo

@Documented @Target(TYPE) @Inherited @Repeatable(ClassInfoContainer.class) @Retention(CLASS) public @interface ClassInfo
Contem as anotacoes informativas pertinentes a classe que ela e implementada
Since:
1.0-SNAPSHOT
Author:
Deiv
